	* fvwm/builtins.c
	* fvwm/builtins.h
	* fvwm/functions.c
	* fvwm/fvwm2.1
	* fvwm/module_interface.c
	* libs/defaults.h
	Add a new global configuration parameter ModuleTimeout to
	determine how long fvwm will wait for a module to respond before
	killing it. Default value is 5 seconds.

