	* fvwm/borders.c (SetBorderStyle):
	* fvwm/builtins.c (do_button_style):
	(do_title_style):
	moved lots of duplicate code into a common function
	general clean up
	ButtonStyle, TitleStyle and BorderStyle commands take effect without a
	recapture

