	* fvwm/misc.c (IsRectangleOnThisPage): generalised version of
	IsWindowOnThisPage.

	* fvwm/windowlist.c:
	* fvwm/stack.c:
	* fvwm/session.c:
	* fvwm/placement.c:
	* fvwm/move_resize.c:
	* fvwm/module_interface.c:
	* fvwm/misc.c:
	* fvwm/menus.c:
